<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَعدا علينا}</span> <span class="c2">(يَعْنِي: الْبِدْءَ)</span> <span class="c3">{إِنَّا كُنَّا فَاعِلِينَ}</span> أَيْ: نَحْنُ فَاعِلُونَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُحَمَّدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{وَعدا}</span> مَنْصُوبٌ عَلَى الْمَصْدَرِ؛<span class="c5"> بِمَعْنَى:</span> وَعَدْنَاهُمْ <span class="c4">[هَذَا]</span> وَعدا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سُورَة الْأَنْبِيَاء من <span class="c2">(آيَة ١٠٥ آيَة ١١٢)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>